<item>
            <title>[LU-16051] o2iblnd: link modification via &quot;ip link set&quot; is not picked up by local ni status</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16051</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As pointed out by Arthur Novik, &quot;ip link set ib0 down&quot; command fails to result in local NI status change to &quot;down&quot; as seen in &quot;lnetctl new show&quot; output.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At the same time, events like manual cable pull or &quot;ibportstate disable/enable&quot;, i.e. IB-layer events, are handled properly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
